Tail
====

1.3.0
-----
Convert to GTK2.

1.2.2
-----
Fix for compilation problems with spaces in paths.

1.2.1
-----
Make sure AppRun can find rox_run.

1.2.0
-----
Stable release.

1.1.2
-----
Added -h and -v options.

1.1.1
-----
Small changes to compilation system.

1.1.0
-----
Switch over to ROX-CLib.
Can specify a title with -t option.
Add a status line giving time & date of last update, suppress with -c.

1.0.0
-----
Stable version.  (No changes from 0.1.7).

0.1.7
-----
Fix drag & drop code to avoid double drops.

0.1.6
-----
Updated menu code.  Reads <Choices>/Tail/gtkrc.

0.1.5
-----
Better debug output.  Save menu accelerators.  Scrolling to end of
window back in, unless truncated.

0.1.4
-----
Fixed bug in memory management.

0.1.3
-----
Use a pop-up menu.

0.1.2
-----
Disable the debug output.  I tried to monitor the file it itself was appending
to...

0.1.1
-----
Don't include sys/filio.h if it isn't there.
Remove code that scrolled to end of window, because it core dumped.
Report error if file can't be read.
